description: PainAway is a fast-acting pain reliever that helps to reduce fever and relieve minor aches and pains due to headaches, muscle aches, backaches, arthritis, toothaches, colds, and menstrual cramps.
ColdRelief is an over-the-counter medication used to relieve cough, stuffy nose, sinus congestion, and chest congestion caused by the common cold, flu, or other breathing illnesses.
AllergyEase provides 24-hour relief of allergy symptoms such as sneezing, runny nose, itchy, watery eyes, and itching of the nose or throat. It is also used to relieve itching and hives.
SleepEase is an antihistamine used to relieve symptoms of allergy, hay fever, and the common cold. It is also used to treat insomnia and promote sleep.
DigestionAid is used to relieve symptoms of gas, bloating, and discomfort caused by gas in the digestive tract.
FeverGuard is used to reduce fever and relieve nasal congestion, sinus pressure, and pain associated with the common cold, flu, allergies, and other respiratory illnesses.
JointFlex is a dietary supplement used to support joint health and reduce symptoms of osteoarthritis, such as joint pain and stiffness.
EyeRelief is used to relieve redness, itching, and irritation of the eyes caused by allergies, hay fever, and other eye irritants.
StomachGuard is used to relieve symptoms of diarrhea, upset stomach, heartburn, indigestion, and nausea.
NasalSpray is used to relieve nasal congestion caused by colds, allergies, and sinus infections.
MuscleRelax is used to relieve muscle spasms and discomfort caused by strains, sprains, and other muscle injuries.
SkinRelief is used to relieve itching, inflammation, and irritation of the skin caused by eczema, dermatitis, insect bites, and other conditions.
HeartHealth is used to reduce the risk of heart attack, stroke, and blood clotting in people with cardiovascular diseases.
BloodPressureControl is used to treat high blood pressure (hypertension) and heart failure.
FiberSupplement is used to promote regularity and relieve constipation. It may also be used to lower cholesterol levels and improve heart health.
VitaminC is a dietary supplement used to prevent and treat vitamin C deficiency, boost the immune system, and promote overall health.
BoneHealth is a dietary supplement used to support bone health and prevent osteoporosis.
IronSupplement is used to prevent and treat iron deficiency anemia and maintain healthy red blood cells.
MultiVitamin is a dietary supplement containing a combination of vitamins and minerals to support overall health and well-being.
ThroatLozenge is used to relieve sore throat, cough, and throat irritation caused by the common cold, flu, or allergies.
AntifungalCream is used to treat fungal infections of the skin, such as athlete's foot, jock itch, and ringworm.
DiaperRashCream is used to prevent and treat diaper rash in babies by forming a protective barrier on the skin.
WoundCareOintment is used to prevent and treat minor skin infections and promote wound healing.
AntiItchCream is used to relieve itching, inflammation, and irritation of the skin caused by insect bites, poison ivy, poison oak, and other irritants.
Decongestant is used to relieve nasal congestion caused by the common cold, sinusitis, allergies, and other respiratory conditions.
AntacidChewableTablets are used to relieve heartburn, acid indigestion, sour stomach, and upset stomach.
MotionSicknessRelief is used to prevent and treat motion sickness, nausea, and vomiting associated with travel, motion, and vertigo.
